NAME
    Task::POE::IRC - Task to install all POE related IRC modules.

SYNOPSIS
        perl -MCPANPLUS -e 'install Task::POE::IRC'

DESCRIPTION
    Task::POE::IRC - Task to install all POE related IRC modules and
    optional dependencies.

      POE 1.0001

      POE::Component::Client::DNS 1.00

      POE::Component::IRC 5.74

      POE::Component::Server::IRC 1.30

